      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAKE NAGAMBIE (9) just ran into one better here on debut before being tipped out for further time to furnish. Has since returned with a dominant victory and looks the runner in this field with the most upside. Rates the testing material. SNITZOND (8) is an honest commodity who has hit the top-four in all nine starts since joining the new stable. Doesn't know how to run a bad race and has to be included. ENTERPRISE ATTACK (3) saves his best form for this six-furlong journey and will be rock-hard fit for this. In the mix. IL CUBO (5) resumes here for the new yard but has tuned up for this with two recent trials and has a handy first-up record. Can run a race while fresh. DOWNEY (2) rounds out the selections.",
